OL,4,G0020FNature: The Classical Collection
OL,5,     GThe natural world has always been
OL,6,     Ga powerful inspiration to
OL,7,     Gcomposers, and this programme
OL,8,     Gtakes us on an evocative journey
OL,9,     Gthrough some of the best-loved
OL,10,     Gmusical responses.
OL,11,G0120FSex Symbols: Talking Pictures
OL,12,     GSylvia Syms looks at the handsome
OL,13,     Gheroes, gorgeous heroines, pin-
OL,14,     Gups and bombshells who came to be
OL,15,     Gknown as cinema's greatest sex
OL,16,     Gsymbols, hearing from the stars
OL,17,     Gthemselves.
