OL,4,G0205FEve and Marilyn
OL,5,     GEve Arnold photographed Marilyn
OL,6,     GMonroe in the 1950s and 60s and
OL,7,     Gbecame the star's trusted
OL,8,     Gconfidante. She talks about
OL,9,     GMonroe and how their friendship
OL,10,     Gdeveloped.
